'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2874] on 13 October 2000 at 5:02:17 pm'!"Change Set:		RWStream-resetDate:			13 October 2000Author:			Michael RuegerFixes a problem with using a RWBinaryOrTextStream for reading objects from internal streams."!!RWBinaryOrTextStream methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified'!reset	"Set the receiver's position to the beginning of the sequence of objects."	super reset.	readLimit _ collection size.	isBinary ifNil: [isBinary _ false].	collection class == ByteArray ifTrue: ["Store as String and convert as needed."		collection _ collection asString.		isBinary _ true].! !